        <p>Populate the selected template with your personal, professional and educational information.</p>
        <h3>Download and Print</h3>
        <p>Presto! Your resume is ready to share!

        </p>
        <form method="POST" action="/">
          <button type="submit" class="button button-primary btn-continue">Continue</button>
        </form>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg">
        <img class="image" src="images\hr-people_4x.jpg">

      </div>
    </div>
